WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.509 --> 00:00:07.170
ULINE's complete line of Convertible Hand Trucks

00:00:07.170 --> 00:00:10.570
has just what you need to safely handle
and move packages and goods

00:00:10.570 --> 00:00:15.889
of all sizes. These trucks easily convert
between a 2-wheel hand truck

00:00:15.889 --> 00:00:19.220
to a 4-wheel platform truck giving
you versatility,

00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:22.720
utility and cost savings in one single
product.

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:27.140
To convert to the platform position,
press the release latch on the back of

00:00:27.140 --> 00:00:27.950
the hand truck

00:00:27.950 --> 00:00:32.059
and slide the frame down the handle. The
truck will come to rest in the platform

00:00:32.059 --> 00:00:35.579
position. To convert back to a hand truck,

00:00:35.579 --> 00:00:38.930
pull the handle upwards and slide the
frame up the handle,

00:00:38.930 --> 00:00:44.260
locking it into the hand truck position. All
ULINE Convertible Hand Trucks offer a

00:00:44.260 --> 00:00:45.690
long list of features -

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:48.989
their lightweight aluminum
construction makes them easy to handle,

00:00:48.989 --> 00:00:53.300
helps reduce worker fatigue and injury
and is corrosion-resistant,

00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:57.329
the wide 18 x 7 1/2" nose plate holds loads steady

00:00:57.329 --> 00:01:02.190
and the wheel guards protect items
being carried. With 10" solid rubber

00:01:02.190 --> 00:01:02.809
or pneumatic

00:01:02.809 --> 00:01:05.970
wheels, you move smoothly on a variety of
surfaces

00:01:05.970 --> 00:01:09.560
and retractable polyurethane casters protect floors and 

00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:14.840
store conveniently out of the way when
not in use. With a variety of styles and

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:15.590
sizes,

00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:19.840
ULINE Convertible Hand Trucks can handle
heavy loads up to 500 pounds in the hand truck

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:20.710
position

00:01:20.710 --> 00:01:25.440
and 800 pounds in the platform truck
position. The Junior model

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:29.360
is 51" high with dual handles and
the Senior model

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:32.810
is 61" high with an anti-slip
curved handle.

00:01:32.810 --> 00:01:39.170
The optional 43 x 12" and 56 x 12"
aluminum platform decks snap on,

00:01:39.170 --> 00:01:43.030
giving you even more versatility to
carry small or odd-shaped

00:01:43.030 --> 00:01:46.250
items while the 30" aluminum nose
plate extension

00:01:46.250 --> 00:01:51.759
provides additional stability for larger
loads. ULINE Convertible Hand Trucks

00:01:51.759 --> 00:01:54.320
are in stock and ready for fast
delivery from

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:58.770
any of our strategic locations in North
America. Whatever your material handling

00:01:58.770 --> 00:01:59.420
needs are,

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:02.980
ULINE has the answer.

